humbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Ff1ab14.jpg&h=c3cd6004&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/5f36db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F5f36db.jpg&h=04cf3497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/44754c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F44754c.jpg&h=ec0fa0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/14f452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F14f452.jpg&h=29259d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/dee17c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fdee17c.jpg&h=52ef79a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/105044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F105044.jpg&h=1380a0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/22d376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F22d376.jpg&h=6bded0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿姐不時向觀眾展示長在其右邊白滑腋下肌膚的小痣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/eabd8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Feabd8b.jpg&h=e96a0c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/efd369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fefd369.jpg&h=ee018665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c4fb39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc4fb39.jpg&h=da898cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 明言要&quot;push up&quot;自己既阿蛆夾出四吋洪溝，實在令人目不暇給，眼睛都唔知要望邊好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/27a9dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F27a9dd.jpg&h=c9d41243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不時拋出可愛雞蘿柚既姿態，教人垂涎三尺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/df48dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fdf48dc.jpg&h=2b8bffcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&sect; 阿蛆不忘展示大腿柔軟度"},{"pid":"71c11e564238d0af50435edef8fff48c87d4e564","tid":1219272,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揚言會不斷push up 自己既阿姐真係有跡可尋<br />\n阿姐早喺8年前既台慶已經破格求變, 訓身大跳濕身舞<br />\n為觀眾大派長者福利 讓大家睇到目瞪口呆<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2d3a9a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2d3a9a.gif&h=aa0f11eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d2772f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd2772f.jpg&h=35b795aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐先以一part 鋼管舞作熱身<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/be5ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fbe5ede.jpg&h=b7fb295f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單人solo 濕身辣舞既阿姐正在蘊釀能旺, 準備施展渾身解素​<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c4129d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc4129d.jpg&h=6915aeb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐正式爆發潛能 水花四起 霸氣十足<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/879ef1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F879ef1.jpg&h=a1eefbe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿姐即使濕身仍面帶笑容, 非常專業<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/174469.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F174469.jpg&h=1a8e0bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n視后胡定欣當年都跟唔上阿姐既步伐<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/b5fe3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fb5fe3a.jpg&h=f8a5ea33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/65935c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F65935c.jpg&h=5fe516ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/c79916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fc79916.jpg&h=f0733054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後阿姐擺出終極老江湖姿態作結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/e6bb8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fe6bb8d.jpg&h=6af8c6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/b5d825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fb5d825.jpg&h=2a34b775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辣舞過後, 仍熱情俯身騷事業安撫眾人</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd2299166aa5ac4341141a7aebbc63cff072a766","tid":1219272,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:02:13.000Z","msg":"樓上啲J圖夠我J幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb1297bbec3ddf29e3009207049f200df332824","tid":1219272,"uid":45167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">保護阿姐</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729616ee3d91d93ef2540a88feb5f531a3ca3552","tid":1219272,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"咁星期日出去唱<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">萬 水 千 山 總 是 情</span><